# Zero runtime deps — the fixture exists only so monad's Ruby adapter
# detects a Gemfile and runs its defaults. `bundle install` on an
# empty gem set is a no-op after first-run rubygems contact (needed
# to write Gemfile.lock), which is why this ecosystem's
# build_needs_network flag is true in the e2e harness.
